title: Ground News - The DNU issued by the government comes into force this Friday: without the Justice having agreed to suspend it
text:
Summary by Filo News The Decree of Necessity and Urgency (DNU) signed by President-elect Javier Milei together with his cabinet of ministers and ministers, comes into force as of tomorrow, Friday, December 29, without the Justice having accepted any request for precautionary measures to suspend it. As eight days have passed since its publication in the Official Gazette of December 21, it comes into force, unless a judicial precautionary measure suspends it. You may … Share menu More
